      "message": "I\u0027m curious what changes if we just take the midpoint?\n\n  \"float2 midpoint \u003d float4x2(P) * float4(.25);\"\n\nI understand that isn\u0027t what\u0027s in the paper.. Does it cause the result to be larger?\n\nI guess what I really want to know is, is this the exact provable value to translate by? Or is it more of an arbitrary thing to help the end result be nicer?",
